                            <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Dolor justo tempor duo ipsum accusam</li>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right text-primary me-2"></i>Elitr stet dolor vero clita labore gubergren</li>
